reviewText: An American Tail: The Treasure of Manhattan continues the adventures of Feisel as he has new adventures in New York. With his pals he finds new adventures and dangers. Tales of Despereaux is a mouse with a great heart and lots of bravery who helps a princess in trouble.

What a great 4-pack movie, 4 movies for a price of one! 2 American tail gems and a great 3rd mouse movie. The 4th movie gives you an idea roughly what the Walt Disney classic of Uncle Remus stories is all about. The Disney movie has not been released in DVD format in America just yet. If it does, the price will be exorbitant! Sigh!
My son is almost 11and still loves the american tail.great family time have not seen the other two but my son said it was great
Most enjoyable. Great for the family.
The dvds are in good condition and the children especially like brer rabbit.
Absolutely wonderful collection of great movies
